1. fillData(final Helper<MenuEntity> helper, final MenuEntity item, boolean itemChanged, int layoutId)

2. helper.setOnClickListener  Not repeat   setonclick
 helper.setOnClickListenerForce  repeat setonclick

3.Because item is a final type control reuse onclick will reuse the final class will not
 change and helper will not change, but the inside of the data do I always set the good so you use this on the line

4.have header or footer not use animation (method:.ani())

